Trusted Solutions & Services

Advanced Chimney Systems is Northern Illinois’ Preferred Choice for Chimney Repairs, Indoor Heating Solutions, and Grills.

Start a Project

Advanced Chimney has been serving Rockford and Northern Illinois since 1984. You can count on our specialists to assist you in choosing the heating system that is perfect for your lifestyle. We offer the highest quality chimney inspections, repairs, and maintenance service in the area.

Make an appointment with an Advanced Chimney hearth design expert today! We will ask you all the right questions to help customize a fire feature to match your home’s unique aesthetics and heating needs.
